      • value

        public DnsRecordState.Builder value​(@Nullable
                                    com.pulumi.core.Output<java.lang.String> value)
        Parameters:
        value - The value of the DNS record. The format depends on the 'type' property. For an 'A' record, this should be a valid IPv4 address. For an 'AAAA' record, this should be an IPv6 address. For 'ALIAS' records, this should be a hostname. For 'CAA' records, this should specify specify which Certificate Authorities (CAs) are allowed to issue certificates for the domain. For 'CNAME' records, this should be a different domain name. For 'MX' records, this should specify the mail server responsible for accepting messages on behalf of the domain name. For 'TXT' records, this can contain arbitrary text.
        Returns:
        builder

For 'CNAME' records, this should be a different domain name. For 'MX' records, this should specify the mail server responsible for accepting messages on behalf of the domain name.
